'''巴拉克拉瓦'''（Balaclava，{{IPAc-en|ˌ|b|æ|l|ə|ˈ|k|l|ɑː|v|ə}}）头套是一种衣物，戴在头上仅暴露出脸的一部分。该词汇来源是1854年的[[克里木战争|克里木战争]]中的{{tsl|en|Battle of Balaclava|巴拉克拉瓦战役}}，围攻[[塞瓦斯托波尔|塞瓦斯托波尔]]的英国骑兵配戴这种头套以应对寒冷的海风。<ref name="Games2007">{{Cite book| last = Games | first =  Alex| year = 2007| title = Balderdash & piffle : one sandwich short of a dog's dinner
 | url = https://archive.org/details/balderdashpiffle0000game | isbn = 978-1-84607-235-2| publisher = BBC| location = London}}</ref><ref name="Shepherd">{{cite book |first=John |last=Shepherd |title=The Crimean Doctors: A History of the British Medical Services in the Crimean War |volume=1 |publisher=Liverpool University Press |year=1991 |pages=296–306 |url=http://books.google.com.ua/books?id=HpCgkcvNiLcC&pg=PA296&lpg=PA296 |access-date=2015-01-26 |archive-date=2014-12-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141215191328/http://books.google.com.ua/books?id=HpCgkcvNiLcC&pg=PA296&lpg=PA296 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Rutt">Richard Rutt, ''A History of Handknitting'', London 1987, pages 134–5.  (Note that there is a misprint in the date of the Battle of Balaclava, which took place 1854, in the original edition cited here)</ref>

== 概要 ==
传统上用羊毛编织而成。现代材质可以选用各种材料，如蚕丝、棉、聚合物、抓绒等。广泛用于户外体育活动。如[[滑雪|滑雪]]、雪板滑雪、雪地摩托、自行车、[[赛车|赛车]]等，以保持脸部的温暖。消防员佩戴防火阻燃[[芳纶|芳纶]]材质的面罩保护面部。电工通常戴抗[[弧闪|弧闪]]的PPE材质面罩。军用版本也称作头盔衬里（helmet liner）。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://knitting.about.com/od/hatpatterns/a/helmetliner.htm |title=Helmet Liner Knitting Pattern - How to Make a Helmet Liner |publisher=Knitting.about.com |date=2014-03-03 |accessdate=2014-05-01 |archive-date=2014-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140413200437/http://knitting.about.com/od/hatpatterns/a/helmetliner.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

警察及軍隊特别是执行反恐、反黑社会有组织犯罪的抓捕、搜查任务时，戴巴拉克拉瓦头套既防护了面部不被高温、闪光弹伤害；又能隐蔽其面貌特征，事后免遭报复。此外，面罩遮蔽了表情，不给受众从中分析、捕捉到佩戴者的情绪变化的可乘之机。俄罗斯的执法人员戴各自的面罩执行特勤任务，被媒体称为“面罩秀”。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2011/09/01/business/global/bp-russia.html?nl=afternoonupdate&emc=aua22 |work=紐約時報 |first=Andrew E. |last=Kramer |title=Memo to Exxon: Business With Russia May Involve Guns and Balaclavas |date=2011-08-31 |accessdate=2015-01-26 |archive-date=2013-06-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130602202402/http://www.nytimes.com/2011/09/01/business/global/bp-russia.html?nl=afternoonupdate&emc=aua22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

[[2014年克里木危机|2014年克里木危机]]中出现在该地的穿野战服、戴面罩、没有识别标记的部队，被称之为[[小绿人_(格鲁乌)|小绿人]]。 

巴拉克拉瓦头套也被用于非法活动，如街头犯罪、[[搶劫|搶劫]]、非法游行、非法占据。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cambridge-news.co.uk/cn_news_home/DisplayArticle.asp?ID=338658 |title=Latest news from Cambridge & Cambridgeshire. Cambridge sports, Cambridge jobs & Cambridge business – War On Terror board game seized by police |publisher=Cambridge-news.co.uk |date= |accessdate=2009-07-15 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120806052916/http://www.cambridge-news.co.uk/Home/War-On-Terror-board-game-seized-by-police.htm?ID=338658 |archivedate=2012-08-06 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

